DarkMouse::
She looked at Black Aracnia. "I still go the shakes, and..my hand.  I 
cut it and it healed right away. Is that supposed to happen?"
She was getting nervous.
~~~~~~~~~~~~

KitKat::
She looked back at Rowdy with fear on her face.  she didn't want to 
know what he meant by pain.  She backed up few steps and pinned her 
ears back.  The fur on her back was sticking up and her tail was 
down. She bared her teeth and let out a low growl. She didn't want to 
turned into what ever Rowdy was now.  But she still wanted her friend 
back.
